Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.001\fs75\c&H0521D2&\3c&HEAE9C3&\4c&H38B04E&\bord5\shad8\pos(760,870)\fad(900,0)}Here Comes the High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,20,,Did you hear about it?{Have you heard the gossip already?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,20,,And have you seen it?{And have you made sure yourself with those eyes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Those two shockingly beautiful eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,20,,Overflowing with startling romance{A shockingly overflowing romance}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,20,,All-consuming{The hottest topic now}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,20,,Inescapable{It's all about this}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.31,Default,,0,0,20,,With a Taishou Era charming lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.07,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The dawn had broken, but the specter of Shinobu and the geisha Kichiji keeps weighing on Benio's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So upset she is, she's even lost her appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.55,0:01:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't even listen to Shinobu's explanations, \Nsince she no longer believes him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,For a change of pace, \Nshe even goes to school after a long break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But what do you know!{何たることか}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All her friends are already engaged, \Nso Benio feels like she's the black sheep of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And then her best and only friend Tamaki \Nalso says she trusts Shinobu no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio realizes that she won't find respite \Nin talking to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Something snaps inside her \Nand she changes her usual route.{何を思ってか土地を変える道を変更し}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,New destination: Yanagibashi.{着いたところは柳橋}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,New contender: Kichiji of the House of Flowers.{飛んだ相手がはなのやきちじ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the strongest win and keep her love! {that same fucking line as in the preview, still just as impenetrable}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Hanamura?{花村のお嬢様}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Just call me Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My... What could you possibly want \Nat our establishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that obvious?{あら決まってるでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some time to kill today,\Nand money to splash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have come. \NThis is not a place for a respectable lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I just wanted to see what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.12,0:02:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one strange lady.{おかしなお嬢様ですこと}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you can come in.{ご苦労様}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?{あなた、いくつ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I am nine years old.{ここのつです}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're in elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are you doing here?{ここで何してんの}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm learning how to dance, \Ntraining to sing and play the lute{/shamisen}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is to be a jikata!{私地方の方が好きなんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... And what is a "jikata"?{地方ってなんなの}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When other geishas are singing or dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,jikata is someone providing the accompaniment \Nby playing lute or drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, sounds like a lot of fun!{面白そうね}\NYou must be the master's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they bought me.{いいえ買われてきたんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They bought you, as... A human being?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I am happy now.{はいでも今は幸せです}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy to have been bought?{人間が売り買いされて幸せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:51.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,0)\c&HF1E8FB&\b1\blur1.001\bord0\pos(730,104)} Episode 22 \N {\fs79.999} Falling Flowers, Blooming Flowers, \N \h                  and Flowers of Love {散る花咲く花恋の花}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Havin' fun, huh?{いいなぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hearing about this trafficking \Nis already strange enough,{人間が品物みたいに売り買いされるだけでも 不思議なのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but how can you also say \Nthat you're happy with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, may I talk about it?{お姉さんお話ししていいんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can tell her everything \Nfrom start to finish.{えっお話して差し上げなさい何もかも}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born in an impoverished village in Touhoku,{私が生まれたところは 東北の貧しい村で}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,where families are forever poor, because the snow and the cold make the crops fail year after year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, girls who are lucky enough \Nto be born at least somewhat pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,are sold to geisha houses\Nto escape from this misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, child, if you go to Tokyo, you'll be eating cooked rice three times a day and you'll finally be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So try to stay strong, alright?\NStay strong...{だから辛抱してくれな、辛抱してくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Da...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Such transactions were rather commonplace \Nin rural Touhoku until the mid-1930s.{このような情景は昭和10年代まで東北の田舎ではしばしば見られ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The smoldering injustice of this social landscape
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,would eventually boil over into an attempted young officers' coup in 1936 and ensuing civil violence. {/February 26 Incident}{no idea why he says "and after that, it became the outbreak of the war" I don't suppose he means social injustice within japan caused the second sino-japanese war though it certainly is so}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But, but... \NAre you really happy to be here?{でもでもそれで幸せになれたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NI can eat white rice everyday, after all.{毎日白いご飯が食べられるから}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In the countryside, we only had it for New Year or during festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still think about your \Nmom and dad, don't you?{でもお父さんやお母さんのことは思い出す でしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I said something I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, they never teach us a thing \Nabout what geisha life is like at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, that was a complete shock, \Nseeing such a little girl here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Young geisha apprentices are called "shitajikko."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also one, \Nas I have been here since I was ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, your soup is getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Benio, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sir, she headed out to school this morning \Nand hasn't returned as of yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely they aren't making her \Nstand out in the corridor all night? {lit: you don't suppose she's been made to stand in the corridor again - maybe he thinks she didn't get the memo that the school is over and is still standing there? idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure she will be brought home soon, \Nso stop worrying and eat.{もうお付きお帰りになると思いますから どうぞお食事を}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing her weird face \Nalways gives me appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where might she be?{どこへ行ったのかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, don't take too long.{ん、はよせい}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You got any ideas, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio is too whimsical for anyone \Nto predict her actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the best diviner out there \Nwould be in dire straits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said. Which means, I guess we have no choice but to ask at Hanamura house for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Second Lieutenant Ijuuin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Benio is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we've not seen her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have no idea where she might be either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, there's one thing I'd like you to explain to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which might be linked to the events of tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind coming over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant, do you know this geisha Kichiji \Nof the House of Flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NKichiji of the House of Flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take your suddenly pale face as a yes.{顔色が変わったところを見るとあじ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I do happen to know her.{はい存ております}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But may I ask why you bring this up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is... Benio was convinced that this geisha \Nis your lover, which worried her to no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a grown man and I'm not in a position to judge you for visiting the red-light district once or twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if another woman is driving a wedge between you and Benio, I, as her father, must take action!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's get straight to the point -\Nwhat's your relationship with that geisha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, don't you try to talk your way out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Lieutenant - \Nyou tell us the truth about Kichiji here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would {\i1}you{\i0} suspect me of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've definitely heard Benio \Nmumble "Kichiji" in her sleep.{でも紅緒さんは寝言にはなのやきちじって言ってるんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hanamura, I wouldn't ever \Nlie to you on such a matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,These last few days, \NBenio's been utterly dejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just stand silent anymore!{僕はもうじっとしていられない}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, even Tenmaru and Chimaru \Nagree with me!{てんまるとちまるもこの通りなんですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Shinobu, explain yourself \Nonce and for all tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is geisha Kichiji to you?\NExplain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to marry Shinobu, Miss Kichiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to go live with the Ijuuins.{あなたに伊集院生きていただきたいのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this because I wish \Nto ensure Benio's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us about your relationship with Kichiji, \Nin all its detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.\NI'll tell you everything.{わかりましたお話しましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}were{\i0} involved with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, do you actually mean \Nwhat you just said?{本気でそんなことをおっしゃってるんです か}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I, uhm...\NWill assist you in any way I can.{できるだけ協力しますから}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.{わかりました}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me just a moment.{ちょっとお待ちください}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:12:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew, I finally brought myself to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can now say goodbye to the Ijuuins forever!{私もこれで 伊集院と永久にさようならが}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all finally over!{そう解きましたら}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite hungry, actually!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,After all...{あと - this and the next two are mostly my intuition since she mumbles while eating - no clue either}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, being a gourmet \Nsounds a lot like my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry not sorry.{残念ながら}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, may I tell you about my relationship with Shinobu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving nothing out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:45.93,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this moment,\Nso I've braced myself and I'm fully ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at this, Lady Benio.{これをご覧くださいお嬢様}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?{この人は}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He is my late husband.{私の亡くなった主人ですあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, though I call him my "husband," we were never officially married.{主人と言っても正式に結婚したわけではありませんけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We only exchanged the vows \Nto never love anyone else. {A promise to stay together as husband and wife until the next life }
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This man hails from the same village as me.{この人と私とは同じ村の生まれで}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:29.17,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.091201\fscx96.18\fscy96.76\frz-8.6997\frx-2.0772\fry-8.2699\xbord3.93\ybord3.87\org(535.94,93.58)\pos(533.75,69.39)\c&H5B5F49&\3c&HCBBDA5&}Terasako Station {寺迫駅}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My fate is not unlike that of most geishas - \NI come from a poor village, so I was sold away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He, on the other hand, \Ncame from a wealthy family in the same village,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,thus, he went to the military academy \Nright after the middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Several years later—when I was already \Na geisha apprentice—surprisingly, I met him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,From then on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we, childhood friends, fell ever deeper in love with each passing day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It just so happened that he was friends with Young Master Ijuuin,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,who had always proved himself \Na kind and well-disposed man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, in the Siege of Qingdao \Nduring The Great War...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:27.66,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}Map of the Siege of Qingdao \N(September-November 1914) {full text is 海泊河\N第一中央隊(英軍\N日本軍\N第二中央隊\N青島攻擊要\N右翼隊\N大正3年9月—11月\Nイルチ\Nビスマルク\N青島\N左翼隊\N第三攻擊陣地\N(11月6日) but I can't be bothered tbh}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When I found out that he had honorably died in battle, I lost my will to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:20.17,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(2200,0)\blur1\c&H2B3030&\3c&HD5D0CD&\fax0.411246\fscx114.82\fscy166.10\frz-18.5274\frx-1.9678\fry1.6692\xbord1.64\ybord1.00\org(702.64,306.8)\pos(690.83,265.28)}Qingdao is ours! {*降島青 - not sure what's first character but it's clear enough as it is - the fall/surrender of ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,By chance, the one who found and rescued me \Nwas none other than Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, he's been helping me in any way he can, \Nhe was always there when I needed support.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he simply couldn't let \Nhis late friend's love die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is how Shinobu and I \Nhave become what we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Shinobu did all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he's not as bad as I thought he is. {/despite appearances, there are good things about him}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, may I assure you that Young Master \Nis a truly caring and chivalrous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course you say so! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an improper thing to say,\Nbut I was also attracted to that side of him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, I am nothing more than a lowly geisha, \None who is never going be with a nobleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if I know that you're going to be the one with the Young Master, I should be glad to give up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I sincerely believe that your marriage \Nwill be the one that stands the test of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kichiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first ever person \Nto make me feel so special. {/talk about me like this}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio...{お嬢様}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see. It's a huge relief to know that you've lived up to my expectations. I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing we've determined Shinobu's character,\Nbut we still, by all means, must find Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.\NUnlike you, my daughter is a lost cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's split up and look for her.{手分けをして探しましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure puts you through a lot of trouble...{君には苦労をかけるなぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, where could she be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you two.\NFind her scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're our only hope \Nat this point, Tenmaru, Chimaru.{あんたたちだけが頼りなんだからね天 マルチマル}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,'Preciate it, bud!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again!{はい、毎度}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rub a dub dub-Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, that's just you, guys?\NYou scared the shit outta me, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why on Earth are you loafing \Naround here yourself, Ushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do? \NBoss is still in there, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really, Ushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rickshaw Man, Lady Benio is calling for you!{お嬢様がおよびですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to celebrate our acquaintance\Nwith Lady Benio, let's have a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I, a professional jester, am going to initiate the lady into the art of performing this traditional song! {very tenuous guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:32.76,Song,,0,0,0,,{fuck it}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And then this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can do at least this much! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this! Ah... \NAh, and then this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{skip}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{skip}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, what do we have here? \NWhat's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A round of applause! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught ya! I said I caught ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally made sure that Shinobu is a good person! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Kichiji?{おい吉次はどうした吉次は}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I called for Kichiji, not you!{わしは吉次を呼んだんだぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, Sister Kichiji \Nis in that tatami room.{それがあいにくと吉祥寺さんはよそのお座敷でね}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then bring her here! Tell her that Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen of 1st Division is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, that room rented her for the rest of the night, \Nso I simply can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all... They're so noisy...\NShe's in the room that's making that racket?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. {nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is her guest?{どちらのお大臣だね}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be some schoolgirl, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Schoolgirl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of schoolgirls \Ngetting under my skin lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, did you not like our drinks, dear guest?{あれまあわるよいだべか旦那さん}{no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, shut up!\NI'll get Kichiji here whatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm afraid that's impossible, Master.\NYou can't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's an affront to the officer of the Imperial Army.\NShe'd rather entertain a schoolgirl than me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please, hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This Kichiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the... \NWhere did these dogs come from?{んだあれどこの犬だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:20:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the dogs of Count Ijuuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijuuin?\NUgh, that bastard again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!{act. don't bark but idk why he says that}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody! Get these dogs off me, somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoo! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Don't just watch, stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Help me!{助けてくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody!{誰か}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can somebody deal with them?{no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll remember this, Ijuuin! \NYou can't get away with it! I'll remember this! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn mongrels! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.68,0:21:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Shoo! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That was too much... They stripped us \Nof everything but the clothes on our back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl Kichiji already said \Nthat we didn't have to pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell didja insist, Boss?{nc whats nushiban}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:22:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Geisha services ought to be duly rewarded... {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. Now I need to find a way \Nto redeem my rickshaw tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I finally found out \Nwhat kind of guy Shinobu is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Yay! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.37,0:22:26.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs200\c&H14110E&\3c&H6FC0DA&}Ahahahah! {might add "kyaaa"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady is as jubilant as can be,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but she can't even fathom the horrors \NLt Col Innen is preparing for her behind the scenes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, the bill for tonight's celebration \Njust keeps growing,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,just as the hangover only hits in the morning. {"as he who laughs last, laughs best." is not bad but I think mine is closer to the og text: laugh in the evening, cry in the morning; in russian, it's "утро вечера мудренее"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio is on cloud nine after clarifying Shinobu's relationship with Kichiji{少尉と吉次の関係がわかって紅緒は有頂天}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and, overflowing with joy, \Nshe invites her classmates over.{心をうきうき身も軽く幸せいっぱいでクラスメイトを招待する}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But fate is a fabric woven by the devil himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,as Lt Col Innen finally puts into motion \Nthe revenge he's been plotting all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.46,0:23:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu's life is at stake!{周囲の身に一台}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See in the next episode of {\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady:{\i0} "Heaven Yesterday, Hell Today."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart;\N I want him to turn around before he leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me that loving glance once again{made up to better match song pacing}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings{/This unfulfilled wish is heavy}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:16.83,Default,,0,0,20,,Just a tomboyish lady who's a little pretentious
